<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<!-- SECTION: PRE-TALK -->
<!-- Duration: 2 minutes | Pitch: 0st | Purpose: Set intention -->
<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->

<prosody rate="1.0" pitch="0st">
Welcome to Session Three: Deep Relaxation Journey.
<break time="1.2s"/>

This session takes you deeper than before.
<break time="700ms"/>
Into profound rest.
<break time="600ms"/>
Into stillness.
<break time="600ms"/>
Into the healing space that exists within you.
<break time="2s"/>

Over the next twenty-five minutes,
<break time="700ms"/>
you'll experience what deep relaxation truly feels like.
<break time="1.2s"/>
Not just surface calm,
<break time="600ms"/>
but the kind of rest that restores you at every level.
<break time="2s"/>

Make sure you're truly comfortable.
<break time="800ms"/>
Lying down is best for this session.
<break time="700ms"/>
Cover yourself with a blanket if you like.
<break time="700ms"/>
You may become cool as you relax deeply.
<break time="2s"/>

If you fall asleep, that's perfectly fine.
<break time="800ms"/>
Your subconscious will continue to receive the guidance.
<break time="1.5s"/>
</prosody>

