<break time="3s"/>

Another breath, even deeper.
<break time="2.5s"/>
And let go completely.
<break time="3s"/>

Good.
<break time="2s"/>

Now, imagine a warm, golden light beginning to gather at the very top of your head.
<break time="2s"/>
This light is pure relaxation.
<break time="1s"/>
Pure peace.
<break time="1s"/>
Pure healing.
<break time="2s"/>

Feel it spreading across your scalp.
<break time="1.5s"/>
Warming.
<break time="1s"/>
Softening.
<break time="1s"/>
Releasing any tension you didn't even know you were holding.
<break time="2.5s"/>

The light flows down across your forehead.
<break time="1.5s"/>
Smoothing the lines.
<break time="1s"/>
Relaxing the muscles around your eyes.
<break time="1.5s"/>

Down through your cheeks.
<break time="1.5s"/>
Releasing your jaw, which so often holds stress.
<break time="1s"/>
Let your mouth fall slightly open if that feels comfortable.
<break time="2.5s"/>

The golden light flows into your neck.
<break time="1.5s"/>
Down through each vertebra.
<break time="1.2s"/>
Releasing.
<break time="1s"/>
Softening.
<break time="1s"/>
Letting go.
<break time="2.5s"/>

Into your shoulders.
<break time="1.5s"/>
So much tension lives here.
<break time="1s"/>
Watch it dissolve in the warm light.
<break time="2s"/>

Down through your arms.
<break time="1.5s"/>
Through your elbows.
<break time="1.2s"/>
Your wrists.
<break time="1.2s"/>
Your hands becoming heavy and warm.
<break time="1.5s"/>
Your fingers tingling slightly as they relax completely.
<break time="3s"/>

The light fills your chest now.
<break time="1.5s"/>
Your heart softening.
<break time="1.2s"/>
Your breathing becoming effortless.
<break time="2s"/>

Down through your belly.
<break time="1.5s"/>
Release any holding here.
<break time="1.2s"/>
Let your stomach be soft.
<break time="1.2s"/>
Round.
<break time="1s"/>
Relaxed.
<break time="2.5s"/>

The golden light flows through your lower back.
<break time="1.5s"/>
Through your hips.
<break time="1.2s"/>
Into your thighs, heavy against the surface beneath you.
<break time="2s"/>

Down through your knees.
<break time="1.2s"/>
Your calves.
<break time="1.2s"/>
Your ankles.
<break time="1.2s"/>
And finally, filling your feet completely.
<break time="2s"/>

Your entire body is now filled with golden light.
<break time="1.5s"/>
Warm.
<break time="1s"/>
Heavy.
<break time="1s"/>
Completely at peace.
<break time="3s"/>
</prosody>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<!-- SECTION: JOURNEY - Theta State -->
<!-- Duration: 12 minutes | Pitch: -2st | Purpose: Deep stillness -->
<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->

<prosody rate="1.0" pitch="-2st">
