<break time="2s"/>

Imagine you are gently descending.
<break time="1.5s"/>
Like a leaf floating down through still water.
<break time="2s"/>
Slowly.
<break time="1.5s"/>
Effortlessly.
<break time="1.5s"/>
Deeply.
<break time="3s"/>

With each breath, you sink a little more.
<break time="2s"/>

Breath.
<break time="2.5s"/>
Deeper.
<break time="2.5s"/>

Breath.
<break time="2.5s"/>
Deeper still.
<break time="3s"/>

You are entering the realm of profound rest.
<break time="2s"/>
A place beneath thought.
<break time="1.5s"/>
Beneath worry.
<break time="1.5s"/>
Beneath doing.
<break time="2.5s"/>

Here, there is nothing you need to figure out.
<break time="2s"/>
Nothing you need to solve.
<break time="1.5s"/>
Nothing you need to be.
<break time="2.5s"/>

You are simply present.
<break time="2s"/>
Simply aware.
<break time="2s"/>
Simply at rest.
<break time="4s"/>

