<break time="2s"/>
You don't need to follow them.
<break time="1.5s"/>
Simply notice.
<break time="1.5s"/>
And return to stillness.
<break time="4s"/>

<break time="10s"/>

You are safe here.
<break time="2s"/>
Completely safe.
<break time="2s"/>
Completely held.
<break time="2s"/>
Completely at peace.
<break time="5s"/>

<break time="15s"/>

In this state, insights may arise.
<break time="2s"/>
Answers to questions you've been holding.
<break time="2s"/>
Or simply a deep sense of okayness.
<break time="2s"/>
Whatever comes, receive it.
<break time="3s"/>

<break time="20s"/>

</prosody>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
